{"tid":2362314,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"日出康城LP10樓書周二上載 首張價單不少於179伙","createTime":"2021-01-11T11:00:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T09:38:23.000Z","uid":150933,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5dbec755f4928644d9c39313b118c8050a8a40d4","tid":2362314,"uid":150933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:00:29.000Z","msg":"南豐及港鐵合作發展的將軍澳日出康城第X期(日出康城第10期)LP10樓書將於周二公布，周二同日開放LP10示範單位予傳媒參觀，LP10價單價錢有機會在本周內公布。<br />\n<br />\n  南豐發展有限公司地產發展部及銷售部總經理盧子豪表示，LP10將於明日上載樓書及開放示範單位予傳媒參觀，料本周四開放予公眾參觀。LP10料周內公布首張價單，首批將不少於179伙，戶型涵蓋2房至3房。"},{"pid":"65c44fb1268aa400fc86749679173abebd15984e","tid":2362314,"uid":150933,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:09:55.000Z","msg":"有咩想問可以隨便問<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tatjaiii\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftatjaiii&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2Bf1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=84e7472d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tatjaiii</a>"},{"pid":"d7215a6c49ca93cce1f04b7cfb7a437b2f837264","tid":2362314,"uid":150933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T12:14:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8a573bfcd0b1e7ad3088192a9021095725ba3d","tid":2362314,"uid":4528,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"65c44fb1268aa400fc86749679173abebd15984e","tid":2362314,"uid":150933,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:09:55.000Z","msg":"有咩想問可以隨便問<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tatjaiii\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftatjaiii&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2Bf1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=84e7472d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tatjaiii</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T13:07:26.000Z","msg":"無野想知 無野想問"},{"pid